  <title translate="true">General options</title>
  <a-keywords>
    <a-keyword>Window Interface Program Options General</a-keyword>
  </a-keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">General options</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px; tabstops:none;"><image src="o-general.jpg" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="11" colcount="2" style="width:654px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Multithreading</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">You can specify the amount of threads Apophysis uses during rendering both - previews and final images - here. You may set this field to the amount of cores your processor has or to &quot;off&quot; if you have a single-core processor. If other applications run very slow or lock up, decrease the value of this field.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">JPEG Quality</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The JPEG quality in percent used for the output images. It is recommended to leave this at 100.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">PNG Transparency</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Enables or disables the transparency for PNG-formatted output images.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Play sound</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">You can specify a sound file to play when a rendering job has been completed here.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Extended render statistics</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">If enabled, detailed render statistics will be shown at the &quot;output&quot;-tab in the rendering window after a render job completed.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Confirm delete</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Shows a confirmation dialog when you delete a flame from a batch if enabled.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Confirm exit</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Shows a confirmation dialog when you close Apophysis without saving your last changes to a flame if enabled.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Confirm stop render</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Shows a confirmation dialog when you cancel the rendering job if enabled.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Save gradients in old format</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Saves gradients in a format which was used by previous versions of Apophysis. (prior to 2.05) This option is there for compatibility reasons.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Always create blank flame</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Disables the template window and always creates a blank flame when clicking the &quot;New&quot; button in the main window menu or the toolbar if enabled.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:172px;">
          <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Internal buffer depth</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:482px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">This sets the buffer depth for all previews. (main preview and mini previews)</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">You may only want to change it from 32bit if you know what you do.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
